  <channel>
    <title>What clerics need</title>
    <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=clericbalance&amp;message.id=10406</link>
    <description>&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;For clerics only.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; And only if you are posting positive ideas to improve our dps to 80% of a druids.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;This is a post on what clerics need to improve thier dps to 80% of a druids.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Also on what utility we need to make us viable.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; If you dont have any positive inputs please dont post.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; This is in response to the druids telling us to come post on our own boards.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; They are pushing to heal anywhere a cleric can with no noticeable downtime and madhaxor has asked us to post our ideas for how we want to dps 80% of a druid on our own board so here we go.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Please only post ideas that help us get within 80% of thier dps.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Or ideas which could increase out utility to more equal them&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;1.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; nukes---theyu have dawnstrike which is 2125 pts of damage.&amp;nbsp; Simple solution here is to give us an 1800 pt nuke---and give it to us in two different forms (ie magic and fire to equal thier fire and ice)&amp;nbsp; then give us debuffs to make it land.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; and with the same negative 200 resist that Eci and glacier now have.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; and since medtime can not be a factor--make it for same mana cost&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;2.&amp;nbsp; Dots---give us dots equal to 80% of thier best ones.&amp;nbsp; So wasp swarm is a dot for 290 a tick for 9 ticks with neg 100 resist.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; so make ours 230 a tick for 9 ticks with neg 100 resist---opens up a lot for me.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;3.&amp;nbsp; quad nukes=give us nukes that hit 3 mobs---easy.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;4.&amp;nbsp; lion strength to add 5% to melee---give us a spell that adds 5% to all magic damage cast&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;5.&amp;nbsp; make our pet persistent---both our pets bite--just makes it so I dont have to recast mine and waste a spell gem&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;6.&amp;nbsp; make our RDS unresistable and make it do 44 pts of damage a hit---80% of nettleshield.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; We would still have to cast it every mob but massive improvement&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;7.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;7 minute snare(80% of a 9 minute one)---everyone tells me that everyone has it already---just give it to me already cause I have not seen this in my spell list&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;8.&amp;nbsp; fixed invis for 12 minutes&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;9..&amp;nbsp; hmm the exp from our rez balances out evac, ports, SOE, see invis, Eb and lev--so no change there&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;10.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; leave them charm and DC--they are about as useful as group HOT.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Please post any other ideas.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;DONT POST ANY NEGATIVE COMMENTS.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; MADHAXOR himself has told us clerics should have a post here where ONLY clerics can post positive things to bring us up to where we do 80% of a druids dps (note there can be no noticeable difference in our dps though so it may take more then 80%)&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;btw, no other class should need any improvements to thier healing to offset this cause we are obviously too weak in dps compared to them.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
