      <description>The summoned hammer has a modified proc rate..somewhere over 500..the Sporalie hammer is somewhere over 600..pretty sure those are real numbers I read somewhere. Most, if not all, augs are at a 0 modifier. Assuming the 500 and 600 are used between a 0 and 1000 ( this is an assumption ) they will proc at (assumption again) 50-60% more often than a 0 modifier.&lt;br&gt;The additional proc is minimal dps, even with maxxed Dex. Though, in a Cleric's cas..any additional DPS is welcome.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Thume</description>
